  //- FIXED LENGTHS
  +content-section(contents[3], true)

    +p In some cases you might need to set fixed length (width) of form controls. In that situation you can use wrapper <code class='l-code-inline'>.form-control</code> and additional class <code class='l-code-inline'>.form-control-fixed-[1-12]</code> to set lengths.

    +demo
      +demo-example
        - for(var i = 1; i <= 12; i++ ) {
            .form-control(class='form-control-fixed-' + i)
              input.input(type='text', placeholder=i + ' length')
        - }
